## Install llm-d

[llm-d](https://llm-d.ai/) is an open-source, distributed inference framework
for Large Language Models (LLMs). It enables scalable, high-performance model
serving across multiple GPUs and nodes, supporting advanced features like model
sharding, dynamic batching, and multi-model orchestration.

![llm-d](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/llm-d/llm-d/61cd025ed8d150c7f9098183d87653dee4305247/docs/assets/images/llm-d-logo.png){:width="300"}

Install `llm-d` [helm chart](https://github.com/llm-d/llm-d-deployer/tree/llm-d-1.0.22/charts/llm-d)
and modify the [default values](https://github.com/llm-d/llm-d-deployer/blob/llm-d-1.0.22/charts/llm-d/values.yaml).

```bash
# renovate: datasource=helm depName=llm-d registryUrl=https://llm-d.ai/llm-d-deployer
LLM_D_HELM_CHART_VERSION="1.0.22"

kubectl apply -f- << EOF
apiVersion: gateway.kgateway.dev/v1alpha1
kind: GatewayParameters
metadata:
  name: llm-d-inference-gateway
  namespace: kgateway-system
spec:
  kube:
    service:
      extraAnnotations:
        service.beta.kubernetes.io/aws-load-balancer-type: "external"
        service.beta.kubernetes.io/aws-load-balancer-scheme: internet-facing
        service.beta.kubernetes.io/aws-load-balancer-nlb-target-type: "instance"
EOF

helm repo add llm-d https://llm-d.ai/llm-d-deployer
cat > "${TMP_DIR}/${CLUSTER_FQDN}/helm_values-llm-d.yml" << EOF
gateway:
  gatewayClassName: kgateway
ingress:
  enabled: false
EOF
helm upgrade --install --version "${LLM_D_HELM_CHART_VERSION}" --namespace llm-d --create-namespace --values "${TMP_DIR}/${CLUSTER_FQDN}/helm_values-llm-d.yml" llm-d llm-d/llm-d
```

Add the llm-d Grafana dashboard for enhanced monitoring and visualization:

```bash
KUBE_PROMETHEUS_STACK_HELM_CHART_VERSION="67.9.0"
cat > "${TMP_DIR}/${CLUSTER_FQDN}/helm_values-kube-prometheus-stack-llm-d.yml" << EOF
grafana:
  dashboards:
    default:
      llm-d-dashboard:
        # LLM-D official dashboard
        url: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/llm-d/llm-d-deployer/f98d3821afd6a36c629a9780bfb3841a67b5d829/quickstart/grafana/dashboards/llm-d-dashboard.json
        datasource: Prometheus
EOF
helm upgrade --install --version "${KUBE_PROMETHEUS_STACK_HELM_CHART_VERSION}" --namespace kube-prometheus-stack --reuse-values --values "${TMP_DIR}/${CLUSTER_FQDN}/helm_values-kube-prometheus-stack-velero-cert-manager.yml" kube-prometheus-stack prometheus-community/kube-prometheus-stack
```





